<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" style="" size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" style="" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" style="" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span lang="en-GB" style=""><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><div style="margin: 0px;"><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><div style="margin: 0px;"><span id="m_-7374277584708053788gmail-m_-1417858540098168688gmail-m_-7331988012953614061m_-5334638735865710201docs-internal-guid-8e7e2af2-3424-7cf0-dabc-c6eb49512b3b">The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our attention which may affect your children.<br><br>I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of hand, foot and mouth disease in a pupil in one of our Year 3 classes. Hand, foot and mouth disease is a contagious, viral infection which spreads if contaminated droplets or bodily fluids are transferred from an infected person. Symptoms include cold-like symptoms such as: loss of appetite, headache, fatigue, irritability, cough, a moderately high temperature, a non-itchy red rash and painful mouth ulcers. Hand-foot-and-mouth disease may cause all of the above signs and symptoms or just a few of them. Please seek immediate medical advice and advise the school promptly if your child is unwell with any of the above symptoms.<br><br>At school, we are taking all necessary precautions including:<br><br>- Ensuring all classrooms are disinfected, including&nbsp;</span>UV lamp treatments tonight and at the weekend (as per our usual deep clean)&nbsp;</div><div style="margin: 0px;">- Good ventilation of classrooms and other rooms<br>â€¨- Daily cleaning and disinfection of the door handles, stair railings, toys, bathroom accessories and food utensils<br>- Unwell children will see the nurse and, if necessary, parents will be contacted<br>- The children have been taught how to wash their hands by teachers<br><br>If you believe your child has hand, foot and mouth disease, please seek medical treatment, follow safety procedures at home and keep them away from school until they have recovered from the illness.<br><br>For further information about hand, foot and mouth disease, please see the link below:<p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify;"><a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Hand-foot-and-mouth-disease/Pages/Introduction.aspx" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Hand-foot-and-mouth-disease/Pages/Introduction.aspx&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1582875106563000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEWiAVDliadanm0LuvW8Xqsyjp49w" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration-line: none;"><span style="text-decoration-line: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/<wbr>Hand-foot-and-mouth-disease/<wbr>Pages/Introduction.aspx</span></a></p><font color="#000000" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></font>Warm regards,<br><br><br>Deborah O'Callaghan&nbsp;&nbsp;</div><div style="margin: 0px;">Head of Primary&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div></div></div></font></span><div><br>The British School Yangon<br></div></span></font></div></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;"><font face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" size="2">www.britishschoolyangon.org</font></p></div></div>]]></td>
